---
import { Card, CardContent, CardHeader, CardTitle } from "./ui/card";
---

<div
  class="flex flex-col gap-12 items-center justify-center min-h-screen sm:min-h-[600px] sm:my-56 my-24 w-full max-w-screen-lg mx-auto"
>
  <h1
    class="text-white scroll-m-20 text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight lg:text-5xl"
  >
    Features
  </h1>
  <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 grid-cols-1 gap-12 sm:gap-24 p-4">
    <Card className="w-[350px] mx-auto bg-black border-primary text-white">
      <CardHeader className="flex flex-row items-center gap-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-md">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path fill="none" stroke="black" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M12 2v20m10-10H2"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <CardTitle>Fullstack Open Web Hosting</CardTitle>
        </div>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <p>Host static sites, client-side apps, and serverless functions all in one place—open, composable, and future-proof.</p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
    <Card className="w-[350px] mx-auto bg-black border-primary text-white">
      <CardHeader className="flex flex-row items-center gap-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-md">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="black" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/><path d="M8 12h8M12 8v8" stroke="black" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <CardTitle>Supports Static & Client-side Apps</CardTitle>
        </div>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <p>Deploy any static site or client-rendered app—React, Astro, Next.js, Vue, Svelte, and more.</p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
    <Card className="w-[350px] mx-auto bg-black border-primary text-white">
      <CardHeader className="flex flex-row items-center gap-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-md">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect x="4" y="4" width="16" height="16" rx="2" stroke="black" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/><path d="M8 8h8v8H8z" stroke="black" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <CardTitle>Serverless Functions</CardTitle>
        </div>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <p>Run backend code with serverless functions for a true fullstack experience—no infrastructure headaches.</p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
    <Card className="w-[350px] mx-auto bg-black border-primary text-white">
      <CardHeader className="flex flex-row items-center gap-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-md">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4 17V7a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h12a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v10a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z" stroke="black" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/><path d="M8 21h8" stroke="black" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <CardTitle>bhvr Partnership & Quickstart</CardTitle>
        </div>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <p>Official deployment partner for <b>bhvr</b>, the fullstack framework. Use Orbiter CLI to instantly scaffold and deploy bhvr apps.</p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
    <Card className="w-[350px] mx-auto bg-black border-primary text-white">
      <CardHeader className="flex flex-row items-center gap-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-md">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2a10 10 0 1 0 0 20 10 10 0 0 0 0-20zm0 0v20" stroke="black" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <CardTitle>Open Source</CardTitle>
        </div>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <p>Orbiter is open source—transparent, auditable, and built for the community.</p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
    <Card className="w-[350px] mx-auto bg-black border-primary text-white">
      <CardHeader className="flex flex-row items-center gap-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-md">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M2 12a10 10 0 1 1 20 0A10 10 0 0 1 2 12zm10-6v12" stroke="black" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <CardTitle>Independent</CardTitle>
        </div>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <p>Built and run by indie founders. No VC, no lock-in, no corporate overlords.</p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
    <Card className="w-[350px] mx-auto bg-black border-primary text-white">
      <CardHeader className="flex flex-row items-center gap-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-md">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M2 12h20" stroke="black" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <CardTitle>Fast</CardTitle>
        </div>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <p>Global CDN, instant cache, and zero build queue. Your site is always fast.</p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
    <Card className="w-[350px] mx-auto bg-black border-primary text-white">
      <CardHeader className="flex flex-row items-center gap-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-md">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M4 4h16v16H4z" stroke="black" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <CardTitle>No Build Minutes</CardTitle>
        </div>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <p>Run builds locally—never pay for build minutes again. Deploy in seconds, not minutes.</p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
    <Card className="w-[350px] mx-auto bg-black border-primary text-white">
      <CardHeader className="flex flex-row items-center gap-4">
        <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-md">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-10 w-10 text-white" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 2v20M2 12h20" stroke="black" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <CardTitle>Redirects & Custom 404s</CardTitle>
        </div>
      </CardHeader>
      <CardContent>
        <p>First-class support for redirects and custom 404 pages—control your site's experience.</p>
      </CardContent>
    </Card>
  </div>
</div>
